channel.title: Fellow Hamachi Possessors
channel.description: Greetings fellow Hamachi possessors. I am looking for somebody to try to get on my server using Hamachi because all of my friends are too "busy". I understand that Hamachi is stupid and inconvenient, but due to the fact that my ISP doesn't allow me to port forward correctly because it is stupid, and that I need to save up still for a VPS, I am stuck with Hamachi. I will only be using it to allow my staff and I to work on the server together. So if anybody is willing to help me out, please pm me and I will give you the download link to my server, and my Hamachi IP and password. I am not giving out this information in the thread because that would be considered advertising. Thank you.
